arnish finished pancakes with tomatoes.<br>Add vegetables (e.g. spinach, pre-steamed leek, mushroom slices or peas) to the unset batter in the pan and use vegan cheese alternatives, as desired."],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","35m","4 pieces"]}